'''自由倡议'''（{{lang-pt|Iniciativa Liberal}}）是一个由{{link-pt|约翰·科特里姆·菲格雷多|João Cotrim Figueiredo}}领导的[[葡萄牙政党列表|葡萄牙政党]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://iniciativaliberal.pt/ainiciativa/|title=A Iniciativa {{!}} Iniciativa Liberal|language=pt|access-date=2019-10-21}}</ref>。它的意识形态是[[古典自由主义|古典自由主义]]，主张更多的经济、政治和公民自由，减少国家干预<ref name="iniciativaliberal">{{cite web|url=https://iniciativaliberal.pt/en/iniciativa/|title=What is Iniciativa Liberal? - More Political, Social and Economic Freedom|website=iniciativaliberal.pt|accessdate=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222051654/https://iniciativaliberal.pt/en/iniciativa/|archive-date=2017-12-22}}</ref><ref name="values">{{Cite web|url=https://iniciativaliberal.pt/conviccoes/valores/|title=Valores {{!}} Iniciativa Liberal|language=pt|access-date=2020-12-19}}</ref><ref name="identity">{{Cite web|url=https://iniciativaliberal.pt/identidade/|title=Identidade {{!}} Iniciativa Liberal|language=pt|access-date=2020-12-19}}</ref>。该党目前在[[共和国议会_(葡萄牙)|议会]]中有八个席位，是在[[2022年葡萄牙立法选举|2022年议会选举中]]赢得的<ref name=":1" />。

==历史==
该党于2016年作为一个社团成立。2017年9月，自由倡议将政党正式成立所需的8176个签名（超过法律要求的7500个签名）交付{{le|宪法法院 (葡萄牙)|Constitutional Court (Portugal)|宪法法院}}。2017年11月26日，成立大会在[[波尔图|波尔图]]举行。宪法法院于2017年12月13日接受了其在葡萄牙政党名册中的注册<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.tribunalconstitucional.pt/tc/acordaos/20170826.html |title = ACÓRDÃO Nº 826/2017|website=Tribunal Constitucional |date = 2017-12-13 |language = pt|accessdate = 2020-12-20}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://eco.sapo.pt/2017/12/16/iniciativa-liberal-ja-e-um-partido/|title=Iniciativa Liberal já é um partido|date=2017-12-16|website=ECO|accessdate=2020-12-19}}</ref>。该党于2017年11月被接纳为[[欧洲政党|欧洲政党]][[欧洲自由民主联盟党|欧洲自由民主联盟党]]的成员。

[[2019年欧洲议会选举_(葡萄牙)|2019年欧洲议会选举]]是该党首次参加选举，最终获得0.9%的选票，未能在[[欧洲议会|欧洲议会]]赢得任何席位。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eleicoes.mai.gov.pt/europeias2019/|title=Europeias 2019 - Resultados Globais|website=eleicoes.mai.gov|language=pt|access-date=2020-12-19}}</ref> 

[[2019年葡萄牙立法选举|2019年立法选举]]中，该党的现任党主席{{link-pt|约翰·科特里姆·菲格雷多|João Cotrim Figueiredo}}在[[里斯本|里斯本]]的[[选区|选区]]赢得了一个[[共和国议会_(葡萄牙)|议会]]席位。该党总计获得67,681张选票，相当于投票人数的1.29%。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.legislativas2019.mai.gov.pt/|title=Legislativas 2019 - Resultados Globais|website=legislativas2019.mai.gov|language=pt|access-date=2020-12-19}}</ref>

2020年7月25日，自由倡议地区委员会主席{{link-pt|蒂亚戈·玛雅·贡萨尔维斯|Tiago Mayan Gonçalves}}宣布自己将参加{{le|2021年葡萄牙总统选举|2021 Portuguese presidential election|2021年总统选举}}，并得到了党的支持。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://liberalmayan.pt/ |title = Mayan 2021 - a alternativa Libera|website=liberalmayan|date = 2020-07-25 |language = pt|accessdate = 2020-12-20}}</ref>

2020年10月25日，{{le|努诺·巴拉塔|Nuno Barata}}在{{le|2020年亚速尔地区选举|2020 Azorean regional election|亚速尔群岛议会选举}}中当选，于2020年11月16日上任。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.acorianooriental.pt/noticia/iniciativa-liberal-elege-deputado-pela-primeira-vez-318317|title = Iniciativa Liberal elege deputado pela primeira vez|website=Açoriano Oriental|date = 2020-10-25 |language = pt|accessdate = 2020-12-20}}</ref>

==政治纲领==
2018年5月5日，自由倡议通过了其[[政治纲领|政治纲领]]，其口号是“更少的国家，更多的自由”<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://ionline.sapo.pt/610907 |title = Parece que não sabem que o muro de Berlim caiu e o sistema falhou|website=ionline |date = 2018-05-06 |language = pt|accessdate = 2020-12-20}}</ref>。该党支持通过协作方式构建，包括通过[[电子邮件|电子邮件]]发送提案，该党还提议减少[[公务员|公务员]]人数<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.dn.pt/lusa/interior/iniciativa-liberal-aprova-programa-politico-que-defende-reducao-de-funcionarios-publicos-9312228.html |title = Iniciativa Liberal aprova programa político que defende redução de funcionários públicos|website=DN|date = 2018-05-05 |language = pt|accessdate = 2020-12-20}}</ref>。[[2019年葡萄牙立法选举|2019年议会选举]]之前，该党提出以下纲领：收入超过650[[欧元|欧元]]的部分征收15％单一税率的[[个人所得税|个人所得税]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.publico.pt/2019/07/08/politica/noticia/iniciativa-liberal-propoe-taxa-unica-irs-15-1879106|title = Iniciativa Liberal propõe taxa única de IRS de 15%|website=Público|date = 2019-07-08 |language = pt|accessdate = 2020-12-20}}</ref>；将{{link-pt|疾病保护与援助研究所|ADSE|ADSE}}扩展到所有葡萄牙人<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.sabado.pt/portugal/politica/detalhe/iniciativa-liberal-volta-a-pedir-adse-para-todos|title = Iniciativa Liberal volta a pedir ADSE para todos|website=Sábado |date = 2019-07-04 |language = pt|accessdate = 2020-12-20}}</ref>；增加公立和私立系统中[[择校|选择学校]]的自由，使其不再与学生的住址联系起来<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.noticiasaominuto.com/politica/1290851/iniciativa-liberal-propoe-liberdade-de-escolha-da-escola |title = Iniciativa Liberal propõe liberdade de escolha da escola|website=Notícias ao Minuto|date = 2019-07-18 |language = pt|accessdate = 2020-12-20}}</ref>；大学可以自由设定录取标准<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.jornaldenegocios.pt/economia/educacao/detalhe/iniciativa-liberal-quer-universidades-a-definir-criterios-de-admissao-de-alunos |title = Iniciativa Liberal quer universidades a definir critérios de admissão de alunos|website=Jornal de Negócios|date = 2019-08-01 |language = pt|accessdate = 2020-12-20}}</ref>。

